metadata.name: CAPPADOCİA TALE
metadata.description:
It is the region that emerged after the soft layers formed by lava and ashes from the surrounding mountains 60 million years ago were eroded by rain and wind over millions of years.

Together with the entire Cappadocia Region, is on UNESCO's list of the World's Extraordinary Cultural and Natural Heritage.

Now it is like a fairy tale land of balloons and horses. everyone will be there before sunrise to spend the happiest moment of their life and experience this moment. marriage proposals, a moment full of wine alone. I always have one of those moments when I don't want this dream to end when I'm there.

Artis: Beytullah ELES 

Camera: Dji mavic 2 pro

Dimensions: 5472 × 3078

Resolution: 300dpi

Location: Cappadocia / Turkey

Date: 019/01/2021

Edition: 1/1
